OL,3,CFamily 'traumatised' as two sentenced
OL,4,Cfor Donegal cliffs murder
OL,6,FA man and a woman have been sentenced
OL,7,Fto life imprisonment by an Irish court
OL,8,Ffor the murder of a man in Co Donegal.
OL,10,FRobert "Robin" Wilkin, 66, was thrown
OL,11,Foff the /Slieve League cliffs on June
OL,12,F25 2023.
OL,14,FAlan Vial, 39, of Drumanoo Head in
OL,15,FKillybegs, and Nikita Burns, 24, from
OL,16,FAn Charraig in Co Donegal, were found
OL,17,Fguilty of the murder, and were
OL,18,Fsentenced at the Central Criminal
OL,19,FCourt in Dublin on Friday.
