OL,6,FDetective Garda David Durkin told the
OL,7,Fcourt that Vial had several previous
OL,8,Fconvictions for road traffic and
OL,9,F"public order-type" offences while
OL,10,FBurns had no previous convictions.
OL,12,FMr Wilkin, a native of Omagh, Co
OL,13,FTyrone, had two sisters and a brother.
OL,15,FOne sister, Irene McAleer, said Mr
OL,16,FWilkins was the eldest of the siblings
OL,17,Fand they "looked up to him" during
OL,18,Ftheir childhood.
