OL,6,FShe described the murderers as "two
OL,7,Fcold, calculating individuals" and
OL,8,Fsaid the sentencing had brought the
OL,9,Ffamily a degree of closure.
OL,11,FShe said the family was "sickened" by
OL,12,Ftheir attitude to Mr Wilkins' life,
OL,13,Fand added that hearing the evidence
OL,14,Fwas "emotional" and "traumatising".
OL,16,FMs McAleer said the family had been on
OL,17,Fan "agonising journey filled with
OL,18,Fgrief, denial and undoubtedly anger".
