OL,6,FShe added: "Now that the case has
OL,7,Ffinished, we feel at a certain degree
OL,8,Fof closure to accept that Robin has
OL,9,Fpassed, although the brutal nature of
OL,10,Fhis death is something that none of us
OL,11,Fwill ever come to terms with.
OL,13,F"This is something we will have to
OL,14,Flive with us that will live us for the
OL,15,Frest of our lives."
OL,17,FShe added: "To sit in the same room
OL,18,Fwith those two very cold, calculating
OL,19,Findividuals has been so difficult.
