OL,6,FMs McAleer said the family would "live
OL,7,Fwith the details" of the "cruel,
OL,8,Fneedless murder" for the rest of their
OL,9,Flives, adding that Vial and Burns had
OL,10,F"dumped" his body off a cliff "like
OL,11,Fhis life was worthless".
OL,13,FShe said listening to "gruesome
OL,14,Fevidence" had been "absolutely
OL,15,Fharrowing" for the family who had
OL,16,Funanswered questions about whether he
OL,17,Fsuffered or if the first blow killed
OL,18,Fhim.
