OL,6,F"As a family this isn't the end for
OL,7,Fus, our grieving will begin now, and
OL,8,Fwhatever way we can navigate through
OL,9,Fit."
OL,11,FMr Justice Paul McDermott said the
OL,12,Fstatement reflected the "pain and
OL,13,Fsuffering" of the family.
OL,15,FHe commended gardai for conducting an
OL,16,F"extensive and very difficult
OL,17,Finquiry", adding that they showed
OL,18,Fprofessionalism in pursuing the case.
OL,20,FHe sentenced Vial and Burns to life
OL,21,Fimprisonment.
